OL,3,GNorth East
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FPartly
OL,6,Fcloudy initially then mist and low
OL,7,Fcloud is expected to extend inland
OL,8,Ffrom the coast. Chance of a slight
OL,9,Ffrost, and patchy fog, for any places
OL,10,Fthat remain clear.
OL,11,
OL,12,CSunday:FEarly mist, patchy fog or low
OL,13,Fcloud disperses. Then bright with
OL,14,Foften large amounts of high cloud, and
OL,15,Fa chance of showers. Slightly warmer
OL,16,Ffor many areas than Saturday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
