OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:FMonday
OL,6,Fbright spells and scattered heavy
OL,7,Fshowers developing. Tuesday and
OL,8,FWednesday dry with bright or sunny
OL,9,Fspells, but perhaps coastal low cloud
OL,10,Ffor Tuesday. Temperatures generally
OL,11,Fnear average inland.
